                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/890.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-09-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 22, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I urgently request authority to insist that all ports be opened, on the ground
                    that the revenues of the receivership are decreased by the closure.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sullivan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
